\section{Deployment}

\subsection{Docker}

\begin{lstlisting}[language=docker, style=mystyle]
FROM python:3.11-slim
WORKDIR /app
RUN pip install uv --no-cache-dir
COPY pyproject.toml uv.lock* ./
RUN uv sync --frozen --no-cache
COPY . .
RUN useradd -m -u 1000 user
USER user
EXPOSE 7860
CMD ["uv", "run", "uvicorn", "server.app:app", "--host", "0.0.0.0", "--port", "7860"]
\end{lstlisting}

\subsection{Hugging Face Spaces}

The environment deploys automatically to Hugging Face Spaces:
\begin{itemize}
	\item URL: \url{https://huggingface.co/spaces/charansaiponnada/ml-experiment-triage-env}
	\item SDK: Docker
	\item Hardware: CPU (free tier)
\end{itemize}

The web interface is automatically generated by OpenEnv.

